The Oversight Committee shall be composed of the following members:
The Secretary of the State Department of Natural Resources or the Secretary's designee;
Two representatives of the Kent Island Civic Confederation;
Two citizens from the 4th election district;
One representative of the Maryland Watermen's Association;
One representative of the Queen Anne's County Watermen's Association;
One representative of the pleasure boating industry;
One representative of the sport boating industry;
One representative from the Maryland Port Administration;
One member of the Board of County Commissioners of Queen Anne's County or the Board's designee; and
One member of the Queen Anne's County Delegation or the Delegation's designee.
